\pard\f0\fs28    {\b 38. A. savranica} Klokov in Schischkin,{\i  Fl. URSS}{\b  23}: 707 (1958). Like {\b 35} but stems 12-25 cm, densely leafy, hispid; leaves 2-16 × 0·5-0·7 mm, more or less straight, thickish, shortly hispid; corolla 3-3·5 mm; fruit 1·7-3 mm. •{\i  W.C. Ukraine} ({\i around Savran'}). Rs (W).
